'''Toongese''' was the native language of the [[Toong/Legends|Toong]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Toong'l/Legends|Toong'l]].<ref name="UAA">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref><ref name="AA">''[[Alien Anthology]]''</ref> Toongs were known to stutter nervously when forced to speak with beings they did not know. Most Toongs were fluent in both Toongese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="UAA" />

